data.description: Unit 603 is the largest (1282 sq ft) and most sought-after unit at Madison with 3 bedrms and 2 baths. Third Bedrm perfect for office or exercise rm, These units seldom come on the market. Madison is a Gated Community in prestigious Park West Neighborhood - Unit 603 is a meticulously maintained and upgraded 3 Bedrm/2 Bath Second Floor Condo in the back of the complex. . There is no third floor above this unit so no one is living above you. Six month lease allowed. Incredible upgrades include new luxury vinyl floors, granite countertops, tile in kitchen and bathrooms, refrigerator, new paint and new water heater. No Carpet! Unit also has a large ((3 by 7 ft) storage area (for bikes, fishing poles, tool boxes, etc). Boat storage (only $250 per YEAR) is available very close to the unit.Madison has numerous resort style amenities to include a clubhouse with pool, fitness center, tennis courts, car wash station and boat storage. Located very close to restaurants, grocery store, athletic fields with indoor pool, dog park and hospital. The famous Isle of Palms beach is only a short drive away.
